Author: Rafael S. de Souza [aut]
Maintainer: Rafael S. de Souza <rd23aag@herts.ac.uk>
Description: 
    Tools for computing and visualizing robust, azimuthally medianized 
    Fourier power spectra from 2-D images. The package supports log- or 
    linearly spaced k-space binning, multiple window functions, and 
    reproducible slope fitting for scale-free structures, suitable for 
    both astronomical and remote-sensing image analysis.
URL: https://github.com/RafaelSdeSouza/PowerSpectR
